title: Call of Duty: World at War (PS2) (NTSC) (Fabio5ilva)
description:
Call of Duty: World at War (PS2)

Region: NTSC

Year: 2008

Confront new and ruthless enemies across the Pacific and European battlefields in the final days of WWII. Fight as a member of the 2nd Marine Division in the Pacific, the 6th British Airborne on the banks of the Rhine, or the 80th Infantry in Bastogne. Engage in multiple mission types including infantry, infiltration, sniper, night fighting and tank assaults.
